4. Interaction Logic

4.1 Node Creation
- Drag from sidebar → drop on canvas  
- Node fades in (200 ms)  
- Plays “pop” animation (scale 0.9 → 1.0)  

4.2 Connecting Ports
- Click‑drag from output → input  
- Line previews while dragging  
- On valid connection:  
  - Spark animation at port  
  - Line animates pulse for 300 ms  

4.3 Error States
- Invalid connection:  
  - Line turns red  
  - Tooltip: “Incompatible port types”  
  - Shakes horizontally (80 ms)  

4.4 Audio Reactivity
- FFT data updates preview in real time  
- Node headers pulse with beat detection  
- Connectors glow brighter on high amplitude  

