6. Performance Requirements

Node Graph
- Must support 500+ nodes without lag  
- GPU‑accelerated rendering  
- Debounced layout updates  

Preview
- 60 FPS target  
- WebGL shader pipeline  
- FFT processed in AudioWorklet  

---

7. Upload Pipeline

Steps
1. Serialize node graph  
2. Convert to intermediate representation  
3. Generate C++ code  
4. Compile via WebAssembly toolchain  
5. Upload via WebSerial/WebUSB  

Error Handling
- Missing board definition  
- Invalid GPIO mapping  
- Compilation errors (surfaced in status bar)  

