9. Developer Notes

- All node types must be registered via a factory system.  
- Node rendering must be decoupled from node logic.  
- Undo/redo stack required (100 steps).  
- Graph must autosave every 10 seconds.  
- All animations must be GPU‑accelerated (transform/opacity only).  

